This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-nxp layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://git.openembedded.org/openembedded-core
  branch: mickledore

  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/meta-arm
  branch: mickledore

  URI: https://github.com/nxp-imx/meta-imx
  branch: mickledore-6.1.22-2.0.0

  ...

Patches
=======

Please, submit any patches against the meta-nxp layer github pull requests at
https://github.com/andrerclaudio/yocto-digest

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-boards-nxp layer to your build
 II. Misc


I. Adding the meta-boards-nxp layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-boards-nxp'

II. Misc
========

This layer provides the base files to bring up the NXP boards to life.   
Supported machines, Distros and Images are placed and its related folders and are quite explanatory, please,
refer to them in order to check what is available to use in NXP board context.